cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with image retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves learning weights off-line using unsupervised strategy (cs.LG) and embedding original descriptors of database images into manifold-based representations iteratively (cs.IR). The paper also mentions experiments on five public standard datasets for image retrieval (cs.MM), and the proposed method outperforms related dimension reduction methods and manifold learning methods (cs.AI).
